reviewText: This is one of the best episodes of the entire Gigantor series.  Gigantor battles  an extact duplicate of himself.  A classic good vs evil story! The famous "Billie Lou Watt" Does the voice of Jimmy Sparks, The controller of Gigantor. Billie Lou as you noticed ( or may have not ) is often the voice of many of the 1960"s and 1970's anime characters KIMBA and ASTRO BOY, and countless other Anime Movies. One of the  Great Anime from the past!!
